          <p class="item-card-para mt-1"><span class="fw-bold fs-4">  <Del class="text-danger"> ₹ <%= item.price%></Del></span><span class="item-card-price fs-4"> ₹ <%= Math.round (item.price-(item.price *(item.offer/100))) %>&ensp;</span><span
